snippet.title: Free The Prince
snippet.description: Free The Prince Adventure puzzle. Try to save the prince using your puzzle skills to solve each platform puzzle.

snippet.title: Moto-X Freestyle
snippet.description: Moto-X Freestyle Do crazy stunts on your bike like the cheese doodle or vertical disco and watch the replay.

snippet.title: Yetisports: Snowboard Freeride
snippet.description: Yetisports: Snowboard Freeride Try to win this race against 10 penguins, earn bonus points by doing crazy stunts.

snippet.title: Free Board
snippet.description: Free Board Snowboard against the clock. Keep the timer from reaching zero by going through the gates.

snippet.title: Free Ice Cream
snippet.description: Free Ice Cream Point and click ad- venture game. You are kidnapped by the ice cream man. Try to escape the building.

snippet.title: Freeway Fury
snippet.description: Freeway Fury Try to drive as far as possible and avoid other cars. You can hijack other cars while driving.

snippet.title: Freegear
snippet.description: Freegear 3D racing game. Get in your car and race against other drivers to become the champ of the tournaments.

snippet.title: SHIFT: Freedom
snippet.description: SHIFT: Freedom Platform puzzle that challenges you to solve the mini games and platform puzzles each stage.

snippet.title: Ninja Dog
snippet.description: Ninja Dog An evil witch turned a brave ninja into a dog. Break the curse by shooting at rotten fruits with shuriken.

snippet.title: Papas Freezeria
snippet.description: Papas Freezeria Manage the icecream shop taking orders, preparing icecreams and keep your clients happy to earn cash.
